# Limitations and Future Improvements

## Limitations
- Leave pass records are stored only temporarily in program memory. Closing the program clears all data.
- No user authentication against a permanent database.
- Staff can only view and approve/reject in the current session.
- No advanced search, filtering, or reporting features.
- Limited to console interface; no graphical interface is available.

## Future Improvements
- Add file-based or database storage to save leave pass records permanently.
- Implement proper user registration and authentication for secure login.
- Include search and filter options for dormers and staff.
- Create a graphical user interface (GUI) for easier navigation.
- Add automated reports and analytics of leave pass submissions.
- Implement notification system for dormers when a leave pass is approved or rejected.
